1. *Odobrenje* za ovaj projekat smo dobili prošle sedmice. (We received *approval* for this project last week.)
2. Nadam se da ću dobiti *odobrenje* od roditelja za odlazak na put. (I hope to get *permission* from my parents to go on a trip.)
3. Bez *odobrenja* direktora, ne možemo pokrenuti ovaj projekat. (We can't start this project without the *approval* of the director.)
4. Potrebno je da predate zahtev za *odobrenje* najmanje mesec dana pre događaja. (You need to submit a request for *approval* at least a month before the event.)
5. *Odobrenje* za isplatu honorara je stiglo pre nekoliko dana. (The *authorization* for the payment of the fee arrived a few days ago.)
6. Nadam se da ćeš dobiti *odobrenje* za kredit koji si aplicirao. (I hope you'll get *approval* for the loan you applied for.)
7. Molim vas da sačekate *odobrenje* nadležnih organa pre nego što započnete izgradnju. (Please wait for the *approval* of the relevant authorities before starting the construction.)
8. Radnici su bili jako zadovoljni kada su dobili *odobrenje* za povećanje plate. (The workers were very happy when they received *approval* for a salary increase.)
9. *Odobrenje* za objavljivanje knjige je stiglo, tako da ćemo moći da je izdamo sledećeg meseca. (The *approval* for publishing the book has arrived, so we will be able to release it next month.)
10. Moram da dobijem *odobrenje* svog šefa pre nego što uzmem slobodan dan. (I need to get *permission* from my boss before taking a day off.)